        <mxCell id="p5note1" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;align=left;spacing=8;dashed=1;" value="v5 CHANGES (2026-07-18 late night, matches sim v0.12)&#10;&#10;AUDIO:&#10;- GAIN knob floor: x1.5 at 0% (was x2), top still x300.&#10;- NEW J201 JFET stage: +6dB, tube-like soft clip (square-&#10;  law 2nd harmonic, asymmetric knees). Second-to-last&#10;  block; only the GATE after it. Linear to ~+/-1V in;&#10;  soft compression from ~+/-2V out; 9V, VREF biased.&#10;- Chain order now: env filter -&gt; 60Hz HP -&gt; 800Hz bell&#10;  -&gt; JFET -&gt; GATE -&gt; output buffer -&gt; jack.&#10;- Dirt is Bazz Fuss ONLY (choice dropdown removed&#10;  from sim; hardware never had it).&#10;&#10;PANEL (slim-down):&#10;- LFO OFFSET knobs deleted: LFO1 unidirectional FIXED,&#10;  LFO2 bipolar FIXED.&#10;- ALL LFO2 pots deleted -&gt; 2 mini buttons + LED readout.&#10;- LFO2 footswitch deleted -&gt; 2 stomps total.&#10;- CV strength set by button-hold (log curve), so CV&#10;  strength trims deleted too.&#10;- Gate trims: behind the &quot;interior&quot; cover in the sim;&#10;  physical internal trims on mux1 ch4-6 in hardware.&#10;  ALWAYS boot at -48dB / 1s hold / 30s fade.&#10;&#10;BOM DELTA vs v4: -1 CD4051, -5 pots, -1 footswitch,&#10;+2 mini buttons. Panel: ~7 knobs, 2 stomps, 4 buttons,&#10;4 LEDs -&gt; 1590BB comfortable, 125B possible.&#10;&#10;OPEN ITEMS:&#10;- LFO2 slow-rate entry is tap-only (firmware window&#10;  ~20s; LED blinks captured rate).&#10;- Verify LED+LDR sweep range on 567 RT at breadboard.&#10;- Enclosure final call at PCB layout rough-in." vertex="1"><mxGeometry height="620" width="410" x="2950" y="50" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
      </root>
